### Component 3: Backend — FastAPI Application

#### [MODIFY] Router structure across 4 modules

**`/auth` router** — Supabase Auth integration + custom OTP:
```
POST /auth/signup/employee    → validate OTP → create Supabase user → insert users row
POST /auth/signup/employer    → create Supabase user → insert users + employer_profiles → Razorpay order
POST /auth/login              → Supabase signInWithPassword → return JWT
POST /auth/google             → Supabase Google OAuth callback → upsert user row
POST /auth/send-otp           → generate 6-digit OTP → store hashed in otp_verification → send via email
POST /auth/verify-otp         → validate hash + expiry → mark used → return verified=true
POST /auth/logout             → Supabase signOut → invalidate refresh token
```

**`/analysis` router** — AI inference pipeline:
```
POST /analysis/cv
  ├── Validate file (type, size)
  ├── Extract text (pdfminer / python-docx)
  ├── Load resume_parser.pkl → extract structured fields
  ├── Load jd_comparator.pkl → compute cosine similarity + feature match
  ├── Generate: obtained_score, potential_score, negative_grade
  ├── Store cv_analyses row
  └── Return 3-score JSON + breakdown

POST /analysis/linkedin       → Parse uploaded LinkedIn PDF → extract profile fields
POST /analysis/github         → GitHub API (authenticated) → scrape repo languages + README keywords
POST /analysis/company-suggest → Load company_recommender.pkl → return ranked company list
GET  /analysis/history        → paginated list of cv_analyses for user
```

**`/test` router** — Communication test engine:
```
GET  /test/mcq/questions      → shuffle 30 questions from DB seed → return question objects
POST /test/mcq/submit         → score answers → update communication_scores
GET  /test/voice/questions    → return 30 voice prompts
POST /test/voice/submit-audio → STT (Whisper-small) → grammar/fluency analysis → return scores
GET  /test/scores/latest      → latest communication_scores row for user
```

**`/employer` router** — Candidate discovery:
```
GET  /employer/candidates     → complex filter query across employee_profiles + cv_analyses + communication_scores
GET  /employer/candidates/:id → full profile (respects is_visible_to_employers flag)
POST /employer/shortlist/:id  → insert employer_shortlists row
DELETE /employer/shortlist/:id → delete row
GET  /employer/shortlist      → return shortlisted candidates
```

**Middleware stack (FastAPI):**
- `JWTMiddleware` — verify Supabase JWT on every protected route
- `TierMiddleware` — enforce Pro-only endpoints (analysis/linkedin, analysis/github, etc.)
- `RateLimiter` — Redis-backed rate limiting (`slowapi`)
- `CORSMiddleware` — whitelist production + staging domains
- `RequestLogger` — structured JSON logging for Antigravity monitoring

