## Risk Register

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| In-house ML model quality insufficient | Medium | High | Set baseline benchmarks early (M3). Have fallback rule-based scoring if model accuracy < threshold. |
| Whisper-small latency too high (>3s per answer) | Medium | High | Pre-warm container. Use async job queue. Set user expectation with progress indicator. |
| Razorpay webhook delivery failures | Low | High | Idempotent webhook handler + retry logic. Admin alert on failed payment events. |
| GitHub API rate limiting | High | Medium | Require user GitHub OAuth token for Pro. Cache API responses in Redis (24hr TTL). |
| Kaggle dataset license incompatibility | Low | Critical | Legal review of all dataset licenses before M3 training begins. Prioritize datasets with CC BY 4.0 or similar. |
| DPDP Act compliance gap | Medium | Critical | Engage legal counsel before M1. Add consent banners and data deletion endpoints. |
